{"tid":1957630,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"求下各位巴絲打幫幫手入來做份綠色建築問卷(阻大家1-2分鐘)","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T13:36:58.000Z","uid":259026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f745bec27d97495afd29b136ec8dd7e320f0ecd","tid":1957630,"uid":259026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"求下各位巴絲打幫手做一份有關綠色建築嘅問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期武漢肺炎搞到人心惶惶，大家都唔敢出街(我都唔敢)，所以只可以靠網上問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係多得中國唔少，依加先來搞D咁既野，累死唔少學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下各位巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n份問卷好簡單，中英對照，全MC，阻大家1-2分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/wuc9ZNfUaF7MTL549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fwuc9ZNfUaF7MTL549&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQylT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=03cdad33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/wuc9ZNfUaF7MTL549</a>"},{"pid":"0d4487c669ece3cbfee197ded026c8978713072d","tid":1957630,"uid":259026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"連登各位巴絲打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4538fa10e88c8874f481a8e9dde6c51b89e71d97","tid":1957630,"uid":259026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88fd4ba9e8d3506d106c9d65b59dd8656319fdf","tid":1957630,"uid":259026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e677fbf80373ecd7393e045ead069ccde18dacb6","tid":1957630,"uid":259026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h